      "solution": "h,w = map(int,input().split())\nboard = [input() for _ in range(h)]\n\ndef is_liberty(X,Y):\n    return (\n        board[Y][X] == '.' and\n        any(\n            (0 <= x < w and 0 <= y < h and board[y][x] == 'X')\n            for x,y in ((X-1,Y),(X,Y+1),(X+1,Y),(X,Y-1)))\n    )\n\nl = sum(is_liberty(x,y) for y in range(h) for x in range(w))\nprint(l)",
